# Project Directory Structure

This is a **Laravel 12 + Inertia.js + React (TypeScript)** application for a psychology/consulting client management platform called **Kosmos**. The stack uses Vite, Tailwind CSS v4, shadcn/ui, Spatie Permissions, Laravel Fortify, and Laravel Wayfinder.

## Root-Level Important Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `artisan` | Laravel CLI entry point |
| `bootstrap/app.php` | Application bootstrap (middleware, exceptions, routing) |
| `composer.json` | PHP dependencies (Laravel, Fortify, Spatie Permissions, Wayfinder, OpenAI client, etc.) |
| `package.json` | Node dependencies (React, Inertia, TypeScript, Tailwind, shadcn) |
| `vite.config.ts` | Vite bundler config for frontend assets |
| `tsconfig.json` | TypeScript compiler configuration |
| `components.json` | shadcn/ui component configuration |
| `phpunit.xml` | PHPUnit / Pest test configuration |
| `pint.json` | Laravel Pint (PHP code style) configuration |
| `eslint.config.js` | ESLint rules for TypeScript/React |
| `.prettierrc` | Prettier formatting rules |
| `Dockerfile` / `docker-compose.yml` | Docker setup for containerised deployment |
| `.env.example` | Environment variable template |

