**Inertia pages vs. controllers:** Several actions render pages under `appointments/`, `clinic/`, `invoices/`, `messages/`, `schedule/`, and `portal/` that are not yet present under `resources/js/pages/` in this checkout. New UI should follow the exact `Inertia::render('вЂ¦')` paths in the corresponding controller.

Wayfinder may generate `resources/js/actions/` during `npm run dev`; treat those files as generated output, not hand-edited source.

